{"tid":720634,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE JUPAS 選科專題介紹：Chemistry","createTime":"2018-06-28T05:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T13:45:39.000Z","uid":69289,"like":6,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"af3d3db726609e7fc881076e83d0d0b0eb3de2d8","tid":720634,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"信相入得黎既學生哥都應該俾連登茶毒左好耐<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post係為左以正視聽，令各位有志向既中學生能夠堅守理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實化學科出路有好多，除左少數出黎做 Laboratory/Education 行業之外，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">更多既係入咗藥廠/醫務化驗/科研</span><br />\n<br />\n有人話呢科係乞食，但其實只要Google一下，會發現好多科目，下至人文學科 BA / 普通商科 Business / 資訊科技 CS，上至土木工程CIVIL / 電機工程 EE / 物理治療 PT / 法學 LLB 等，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多都俾連登/高登仔鳩吹飽和近十年之久</span></span><br />\n<br />\n或者你會見過好多engine巴打將錢掛係口邊，說穿了係佢地既理想一早已經係入學時冇咗，依家窮到只會講錢，家上飽和既風氣泛濫，出黎付出既勞力慢慢同收入成反比<br />\n<br />\n有時會俾讀藥劑既朋友問返我轉頭，講真化學既野真係比佢地專好多，好多時都會借notes俾佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係R晒頭唔知佢有幾多冇學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n化學黎講 HKU &gt; POLYU &gt; CU = UST &gt;&gt;&gt; CITYU &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; BU<br />\n<br />\nHKU\tJS6901\tBachelor of Science<br />\nPolyU\tJS3997\tBSc (Hons) in Chemical Technology<br />\nCUHK\tJS4601\tScience<br />\nHKUST\tJS5100\tScience<br />\nHKUST\tJS5101\tInternational Research Enrichment<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後俾少少Scientist 意示圖大家睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uncw.edu/chem/images/chemistry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funcw.edu%2Fchem%2Fimages%2Fchemistry.jpg&h=d17c4b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.quintessence.com.cy/udata/contents/images/Services/Training-Program/Certified%20Laboratory%20Manager.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.quintessence.com.cy%2Fudata%2Fcontents%2Fimages%2FServices%2FTraining-Program%2FCertified%2520Laboratory%2520Manager.jpg&h=6e7e11b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.economiematin.fr/img/recherche-developpement-depenses-chine-coree-japon-ue-usa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.economiematin.fr%2Fimg%2Frecherche-developpement-depenses-chine-coree-japon-ue-usa.jpg&h=43a8dd02&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4a4ba42ed597853c5d888a9cbe553a607b093ef3","tid":720634,"uid":78166,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/132427_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F132427_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=301b5f45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36563a2961e1bd37b4366c37f849392d4949622a","tid":720634,"uid":4526,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"唉我知我地全部都死廢西, 點及你咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文即係化學科技高級文憑<br />\n<br />\n聽個名都知勁野啦<br />\n<br />\n化學都已經猛料啦, d乜撚野核彈呀原子彈呀全部都係化學野<br />\n<br />\n閣下讀完之後整番幾粒原子彈出黎周圍炸都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ne家仲要化學後面有個科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n科技wor, 緊係勁野黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得科技兩隻字o既通常都好撚威威, 乜撚野納米科技資訊科技, 聽個名都知勁野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ne家仲要化學科技, 威過威士忌啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地d普通化學家識溝下oxygen, hydrogen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你? 身為化學科技家, 玩到d乜撚野原子分子中子精子識跳舞都仲得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地廢鳩美國佬十鳩幾年前學人玩化學, 掟粒原子彈落去炸日本, 先炸得爆一個濕鳩廣島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你整出黎個粒原子彈, 炸爆成個地球仲得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你仲要讀化學科技高級文憑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n化學科技已經夠哂屈機, 你e家仲要高級o既化學科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地讀化學科技大學學位個班廢鳩, 冇錯都識得玩到d原子分子中子精子識飛識跳舞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢地跳個d, 頂多係泡菜果個傻西呀叔個d郁屎忽舞, 又垃圾又低級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你跳個d, 直頭係華爾茲, 係芭蕾舞, 簡直都唔同level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係1 o既話, 佢地直頭係0都不如, 簡直係負數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本chem tech hd就係神科中o既神科, 屈機中o既屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個d乜撚野medic, law, or even chem tech degree<br />\n<br />\n算鳩數啦, 咪撚出黎獻醜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係chem tech hd面前, 你地連屎都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返屋企打飛機算鳩數啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd宇宙最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd稱霸銀河系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d051623848f5d5f506f1d54f426c0b0de600f9a4","tid":720634,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"我讀完chem 之後，女多識多左"},{"pid":"320b557962af2b73b65f7ccb1d7b0244dc016c61","tid":720634,"uid":135445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"製毒個班人其實係咪讀chem出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a805af9702c3b853333756566554f279f4437383","tid":720634,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d051623848f5d5f506f1d54f426c0b0de600f9a4","tid":720634,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201