rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本chem tech hd就係神科中o既神科, 屈機中o既屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個d乜撚野medic, law, or even chem tech degree<br />\n<br />\n算鳩數啦, 咪撚出黎獻醜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係chem tech hd面前, 你地連屎都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返屋企打飛機算鳩數啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd宇宙最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nchem tech hd稱霸銀河系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:47:42.000Z","msg":"長青巴打依家讀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35587ed7d1c7b299f980c1be025bcaeda93c2bf6","tid":720634,"uid":171509,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"Hku 6901 sci仲有一樣好<br />\n就係夠彈性<br />\n即係flexible<br />\n無gpa要求任意轉major<br />\n又或者想double major都得<br />\n可以major chem+finance<br />\n可以major maths+中文<br />\n就我所知<br />\n科大中大都係唔得<br />\n全部要交表申請<br />\n七成唔批"},{"pid":"f99125bf21ed2b2f72e5511aec828ba69936c16f","tid":720634,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a542feba00e59a285e8a74c4485329b52cfc713","tid":720634,"uid":4526,"like"